      "patch": "@@ -36,6 +36,17 @@ <h1>capnwasm <span class=\"dim\">RPC bench</span></h1>\n       </nav>\n     </header>\n \n+    <noscript>\n+      <p style=\"background:#2a1a16;border:1px solid #5a2c1f;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 16px;color:#ffa726;font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n+        The RPC bench connects two WebSocket sessions and runs three workloads &mdash;\n+        JavaScript is required. The rest of the site\n+        (<a href=\"./\" style=\"color:inherit;text-decoration:underline\">landing</a>,\n+        <a href=\"./honest.html\" style=\"color:inherit;text-decoration:underline\">honest comparison</a>,\n+        <a href=\"./inspect.html\" style=\"color:inherit;text-decoration:underline\">wire inspector</a>)\n+        is static and works without JS.\n+      </p>\n+    </noscript>\n+\n     <div id=\"server-status\" class=\"server-status\" role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\">\n       <span id=\"server-dot\" class=\"dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n       <span id=\"server-msg\">Checking RPC server&hellip;</span>"
